191 //calculate cost between to reach child node if travelling through parent node
192  double calculate_cost (node* parent_node, node* child_node) //add check if node is in obstacle
193  {
194  double cost;
195  if (check_line_obstacle(parent_node->point,child_node->point)) {
196  cost=INFINITY;
197  } else if(parent_node->parent == NULL) {
198  cost=get_dist(parent_node->point,child_node->point);
199  } else {
200  cost=calculate_cost(parent_node->parent,parent_node)+get_dist(parent_node->point,child_node->point);
201  }
202  return(cost);
203  }
204 //get cost of given node
205  double get_cost(node *temp_node)
206  {
207  double cost;
208  if(temp_node->parent==NULL){
209  cost=root->cost;
210  } else {
211  cost=calculate_cost(temp_node->parent,temp_node);
212  temp_node->cost=cost;
213  }
214  return(cost);
215  }

285  //function to find lowest cost neighbours of new point
286  node* check_neighbours (geometry_msgs::Point new_point){
287  if (debugging){
288  ROS_INFO("I've entered check neighbours");
289  }
290  neighbours.clear();
291  double cost_from_neighbour,total_cost;
292  double lowest_cost=INFINITY;
293  double x_diff,y_diff;
294  find_neighbours(new_point);
295  node* lowest_cost_neighbour=NULL;
296  for (int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
297  x_diff=new_point.x-neighbours[i]->point.x;
298  y_diff=new_point.y-neighbours[i]->point.y;
299  if (abs(x_diff) <= node_dist && abs(y_diff)<=node_dist){
300  cost_from_neighbour=sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2));
301  if(cost_from_neighbour <= node_dist && !check_line_obstacle(new_point,neighbours[i]->point)){
302  total_cost=get_cost(neighbours[i])+cost_from_neighbour;
303  if (total_cost < lowest_cost){
304  lowest_cost_neighbour=neighbours[i];
305  lowest_cost=total_cost;
306  }
307  }
308  }
309  }
310 
311  return(lowest_cost_neighbour);
312  }

315  void rewire_root_neighbours (node* test_node) {

319 
320  double total_cost;

323  test_node->cost=INFINITY;

328  find_neighbours(test_node->point);
329 
330  for (int i = 0; i < neighbours.size();i++){

342  add_to_root_queue(neighbours[i]);

344  }

347  }

349  if(test_node!=root){
350

352 
353  test_node->cost=INFINITY;

431  //function to find neighbours based on grid-based-spacial indexing
432  void find_neighbours(geometry_msgs::Point temp_point){
433  if (debugging){
434  ROS_INFO("I've entered find_neighbours");
435  }
436  int lower_x_grid,upper_x_grid,lower_y_grid,upper_y_grid;
437  path_planning::grid_cell grid=find_grid_cell_for_spatial_indexing(temp_point);
438 
439  neighbours.clear();
440 
441  int search_width=0;
442  while(neighbours.empty()){
443  search_width++;
444  //restrict grid exceeding vector bounds
445  if((grid.x-search_width)<0){
446  lower_x_grid=0;
447  } else {
448  lower_x_grid=grid.x-search_width;
449  }
450  if((grid.x+search_width)>(GRID_WIDTH-1)){
451  upper_x_grid=(GRID_WIDTH-1);
452  } else{
453  upper_x_grid=grid.x+search_width;
454  }
455  if((grid.y-search_width)<0){
456  lower_y_grid=0;
457  } else {
458  lower_y_grid=grid.y-search_width;
459  }
460  if((grid.y+search_width)>(GRID_HEIGHT-1)){
461  upper_y_grid=(GRID_HEIGHT-1);
462  } else {
463  upper_y_grid=grid.y+search_width;
464  }
465  //ROS_INFO("X range (%d,%d)",lower_x_grid,upper_x_grid);
466  //ROS_INFO("Y range (%d,%d)",lower_y_grid,upper_y_grid);
467 
468  for(int i=lower_x_grid;i <= upper_x_grid;i++){
469  for (int j=lower_y_grid;j <=upper_y_grid;j++){
470  //ROS_INFO("Checking grid (%d,%d)",i,j);
471  for(int k=0; k < spatial_grid[i][j].size();k++){
472  //ROS_INFO("spacial_index (%d,%d) point (%lf,%lf)",i,j,spatial_grid[i][j].at(k)->point.x,spatial_grid[i][j].at(k)->point.y);
473  neighbours.push_back(spatial_grid[i][j].at(k));
474  }
475  }
476  }
477  }
478  /*ROS_INFO("number of neighbours found %d",neighbours.size());
479  for(int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
480  ROS_INFO("neighbours (%.2lf,%.2lf)",neighbours[i]->point.x,neighbours[i]->point.y);
481  }*/
482  if (debugging){
483  ROS_INFO("im leaving find neighbour");
484  }

515  //function to determine if goal is found
516  void is_goal_found(){
517  if (debugging){
518  ROS_INFO("I've entered is goal found");
519  }
520  if (get_dist(root->point,goal) > goal_radius){
521  goal_list.clear();
522  double x_diff,y_diff,cost_to_goal;
523  find_neighbours(goal);
524  for (int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
525  x_diff=goal.x-neighbours[i]->point.x;
526  y_diff=goal.y-neighbours[i]->point.y;
527  if (abs(x_diff) <= goal_radius && abs(y_diff) <= goal_radius){
528  cost_to_goal=sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2));

530  goal_found=true;

601  //function to if check line between points is free on map. Based on Bresenham's lins algorithm
602  bool check_line_obstacle (geometry_msgs::Point point_1, geometry_msgs::Point point_2) {
603  if (debugging){
604  ROS_INFO("I've entered check line obstacle");
605  }
606  geometry_msgs::Point test_point_1,test_point_2;
607  path_planning::grid_cell grid_1,grid_2,grid_1_test,grid_2_test;
608  int difference_x,difference_y;
609  int map_test;
610  double grad, c,x_test,y_test,angle;
611  if(point_1.x > point_2.x){
612  test_point_1=point_2;
613  test_point_2=point_1;
614  }else {
615  test_point_1=point_1;
616  test_point_2=point_2;
617  }
618  grad=(test_point_2.y-test_point_1.y)/(test_point_2.x-test_point_1.x);
619  c=(test_point_2.y-grad*test_point_2.x);
620  angle=atan(grad);
621 
622  grid_1=find_grid_cell(test_point_1);
623  grid_2=find_grid_cell(test_point_2);
624  difference_x=grid_2.x-grid_1.x;
625  difference_y=grid_2.y-grid_1.y;
626  if (test_point_1.x==test_point_2.x){
627  if (difference_y >= 0) {
628  for(int i = grid_1.y+1; i < grid_1.y+difference_y+1; i++) {
629  grid_2_test.x=grid_2.x;
630  grid_1_test.x=grid_1.x;
631  grid_2_test.y=i;
632  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
633  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
634  return(true);
635  }
636  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
637  return(true);
638  }
639  }
640  } else if (difference_y < 0){
641  for(int i = grid_1.y; i > grid_2.y; i--) {
642  grid_2_test.x=grid_2.x;
643  grid_1_test.x=grid_1.x;
644  grid_2_test.y=i;
645  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
646  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
647  return(true);
648  }
649  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
650  return(true);
651  }
652  }
653  }
654  } else if (difference_y >= 0) {
655  if (angle < PI/4){
656  for(int i = grid_1.x+1; i < grid_1.x+difference_x+1; i++) {
657  y_test=(grad*i*map_resolution)+c;
658  grid_2_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
659  grid_1_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
660  grid_2_test.x=i;
661  grid_1_test.x=i-1;
662  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
663  return(true);
664  }
665  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
666  return(true);
667  }
668  }
669  } else {
670  for(int i = grid_1.y+1; i < grid_1.y+difference_y+1; i++) {
671  x_test=((i*map_resolution)-c)/grad;
672  grid_2_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
673  grid_1_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
674  grid_2_test.y=i;
675  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
676  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
677  return(true);
678  }
679  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
680  return(true);
681  }
682  }
683  }
684  } else if (difference_y<0) {
685  if (angle > -PI/4){
686  for(int i = grid_1.x+1; i < grid_1.x+difference_x+1; i++) {
687 
688  y_test=(grad*i*map_resolution)+c;
689  grid_2_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
690  grid_1_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
691  grid_2_test.x=i;
692  grid_1_test.x=i-1;
693  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
694  return(true);
695  }
696  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
697  return(true);
698  }
699  }
700  } else {
701  for(int i = grid_1.y; i > grid_2.y; i--) {
702  x_test=((i*map_resolution)-c)/grad;
703  grid_2_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
704  grid_1_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
705  grid_2_test.y=i;
706  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
707  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
708  return(true);
709  }
710  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
711  return(true);
712  }
713  }
714  }
715 
716  }
717  /*if (debugging){
718  ROS_INFO("I've exited check line obstacle");
719  }*/
720  return(false);
721 }
722 
723  //function to check map if map grid cell is occupied
724  bool check_grid_for_obs (path_planning::grid_cell grid) {
725  int map_array_value=grid.y*map_width+grid.x;
726  if (map[map_array_value] > OBSTACLE_THRESHOLD || map[map_array_value] == -1) {
727  return(true);
728  } else {
729  return (false);
730  }
731  }
732 
733  //function to add node to spatial index
734  void add_to_spatial_index(node* temp_node){
735  if (debugging){
736  ROS_INFO("I've entered add_to_spatial_index");
737  }
738  path_planning::grid_cell grid=find_grid_cell_for_spatial_indexing(temp_node->point);
739  spatial_grid[grid.x][grid.y].push_back(temp_node);
740  }
741 
742  //function to update neighbour radius based on number of nodes in environment
743  void update_neighbour_radius(){
744  neighbour_radius=sqrt((SEARCH_AREA*double (density))/(PI*double(node_list.size())));
745  if (neighbour_radius<node_dist){
746  neighbour_radius=node_dist;
747  }
748  }
749 
750  //function to check if node density less that max density
751  bool check_node_density(){
752  if (neighbours.size() > density){
753  return (false);
754  } else {
755  return(true);
756  }
757  }
758 
759  //function to test distance between test point and node to determine if greater than node_dist
760  bool node_dist_check(geometry_msgs::Point test_point, node* closest) {
761  double dist=get_dist(closest->point,test_point);
762  if (dist > node_dist){
763  return(true);
764  } else {
765  return(false);
766  }
767  }
768 
769  double get_dist(geometry_msgs:: Point point_1, geometry_msgs::Point point_2){
770  double x_diff;
771  double y_diff;
772  double dist;
773  x_diff=point_1.x-point_2.x;
774  y_diff=point_1.y-point_2.y;
775  return(sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2)));
776  }

778  //function to move the of the tree to the provided node
779  void change_root(node* new_root){
780  int node_list_index;
781  remove_child_from_parent(new_root);
782  new_root->children.push_back(root);
783  root->parent=new_root;
784  new_root->parent=NULL;
785  new_root->cost=0;
786  root->cost=calculate_cost(root->parent,root);
787  for(int i=0;i<node_list.size();i++){
788  if(node_list[i]==new_root){
789  node_list_index=i;
790  }
791  }
792  node_list[0]=new_root;
793  node_list[node_list_index]=root;
794  root=new_root;
795  root_point.x=root->point.x;
796  root_point.y=root->point.y;
797  //rewire_neighbours(root);
798  }

869  //function to control number of time rewiring of random nodes is performed
870  void rewire_random_nodes(){
871  for(int i=0;i<25;i++){

873  break;

876  qr.pop_front();

885  }

887  qs.pop_front();
888  }
